Not-Sahil-Raja/Agrico.summary: The Agrico repository has seen significant refactoring of various components, including the App component, API calls, PopularArticle component, feedback system, and marketplace, to improve responsiveness, functionality, and overall user experience. The project has also added new features, such as a functional dashboard, payment processing, and order and cart systems, as well as implemented authentication using Clerk and refactored routing, imports, and file uploads. Additionally, the repository has undergone considerable code cleanup and optimization, including the removal of console.log statements, unused routes, and files, and the improvement of frontend styling and backend functionality.
